<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>يَغْلِبُ بِالمَكَانِ لاَ الإِمْكَانِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>دَاخَلَهُ الظَّنُّ بِأَنَّ المَاكِرَا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أَمْسَى مِنَ الضَّعْفِ يُطِيقُ السَّاخِرَا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>فَجَاءهُ يَلْعَنُ مِثْلَ الأَوَّلِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>عِدَادَ مَا في الأَرْضِ مِنْ مُغَفَّلِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَعَصَفَ الثَّعْلَبُ بِالضَّعِيفِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>عَصْفَ أَخِيهِ الذِّيبِ بِالخَرُوفِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَقَالَ لي في دَمِكَ المَسْفُوكِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>تَسْلِيَةٌ عَن خَيْبَتي في الدِّيكِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>فَالْتَفَتَ الدِّيكُ إِلى الذَّبِيحِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَقَالَ قَوْلَ الْعَارِفِ الْفَصِيحِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>مَا كُلُّنَا يَنْفَعُهُ لِسَانُهْ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>في النَّاسِ مَنْ يُنْطِقُهُ مَكَانُهْ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c3">{أَمِيرُ الشُّعَرَاء / أَحْمَد شَوْقِي بِتَصَرُّف}</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>الأَحْمَقُ عِنْدَمَا يُصْبِحُ حَكَمَاً<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>تَنَازَعَ الْغَزَالُ وَالخَرُوفُ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَقَالَ كُلٌّ إِنَّهُ ظَرِيفُ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>فَأَبْصَرَا التَّيْسَ فَظَنَّا أَنَّهُ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>أَعْطَاهُ عَقْلاً مَن أَطَالَ ذِقْنَهُ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>فَكَلَّفَاهُ أَنْ يَبْحَثَ في الْفَلاَ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>